# Chun ha tn ct
data.columns = [col.lower().strip() for col in data.columns]

# X l ngy thng an ton
if 'year' in data.columns and 'month' in data.columns:
    data['day'] = 1
    data['year'] = pd.to_numeric(data['year'], errors='coerce')
    data['month'] = pd.to_numeric(data['month'], errors='coerce')
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data[['year', 'month', 'day']], errors='coerce')
elif 'date' in data.columns:
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')

# Xa dng li ngy thng
data = data.dropna(subset=['date'])

# Gom nhm theo thng (Aggregation)
df_agg = data.groupby('date').agg({
    'units_sold': 'sum',
    'stock_available': 'sum',
    'discount_percent': 'mean',
    'economic_indicator': 'mean',
    'competitor_activity': 'mean',
    'lead_time_days': 'mean'
}).asfreq('MS').fillna(0)

print(f"\n D liu sau khi cng gp ({len(df_agg)} thng):")
print(df_agg.head())

  1. Trong bi cnh Kinh t suy thoi (economic_indicator thp), nu i th tn cng mnh (competitor_activity cao), doanh s ca chng ta c b st gim nghim trng hn so vi khi kinh t tt khng?

# 1. Chia nhm cho Kinh t v i th
df_agg['Eco_Bin'] = pd.qcut(df_agg['economic_indicator'], q=3, labels=['Kinh t Yu', 'Kinh t TB', 'Kinh t Mnh'])
df_agg['Comp_Bin'] = pd.qcut(df_agg['competitor_activity'], q=3, labels=['i th Yu', 'i th TB', 'i th Mnh'])

# 2. Tnh doanh s trung bnh cho tng cp
pivot_table = df_agg.pivot_table(index='Eco_Bin', columns='Comp_Bin', values='units_sold', aggfunc='mean')

# 3. V Heatmap
plt.figure(figsize=(8, 6))
sns.heatmap(pivot_table, annot=True, fmt=',.0f', cmap='YlOrRd', linewidths=1)
plt.title('Doanh s trung bnh theo Bi cnh Kinh t & Cnh tranh')
plt.xlabel('Hot ng ca i th')
plt.ylabel('Tnh hnh Kinh t')
plt.show()

Da trn phn tch bin bin thin ca doanh s trong ma trn ri ro, cho thy c hai yu t u c tc ng mc tng ng nhau, nhng Kinh t vn l yu t nn tng quan trng hn.

iu ny gi rng chin lc kinh doanh ca cng ty cn u tin kh nng thch ng vi cc chu k kinh t v m (Macro-economic cycles) hn l ch tp trung i ph vi cc ng thi ngn hn ca i th.

  1. Khi kinh t kh khn (ch s thp), khch hng c tr nn nhy cm hn vi gi khng? Liu gim gi (discount_percent) c hiu qu hn trong thi k kinh t yu?
  • Mc tiu: Phn tch tc ng tng tc (Interaction Effect) gia bi cnh kinh t v m v chin lc gi ln doanh s bn hng.

Bi cnh Kinh t l yu t chi phi hiu qu khuyn mi:

Trong giai on Kinh t Yu, khch hng tht cht chi tiu, khin cc chng trnh khuyn mi pht huy hiu qu tch cc (ng xu hng dng).

Ngc li, khi Kinh t Tt, khch hng t quan tm n gi hn, khin vic gim gi tr nn km hiu qu.

  1. Liu vic duy tr mc tn kho cao c gip rt ngn thi gian giao hng khng? Ti mc lead_time no v stock no th doanh s (units_sold) t nh?

# Chia Lead Time thnh 3 mc: Nhanh - Bnh thng - Chm
# Lu : Lead tim e bin ng t nn dng cut hoc qcut ty d liu
try:
    df_agg['Delivery_Speed'] = pd.qcut(df_agg['lead_time_days'], q=3, labels=['Giao Nhanh', 'Giao TB', 'Giao Chm'])

Nhn xt

Phn tch d liu cho thy vic tng lng tn kho khng gip ci thin tc giao hng, tri li cn c xu hng lm tng nh thi gian x l n hng (tng quan dng), gi cc vn v hiu sut qun l kho khi qu ti.

V mt hiu qu kinh doanh, doanh s t nh ti mc Tn kho Thp, cho thy m hnh vn hnh hin ti ph hp vi chin lc 'Tinh gn' (Lean) hn l chin lc 'D tr' (Stockpiling). Vic duy tr tn kho cao nhng tc giao hng khng ci thin (Giao TB) dn n kt qu doanh s thp nht (Vng ri ro).

Khuyn ngh: Cn u tin gim mc tn kho an ton gii phng dng tin, ng thi tp trung ci thin quy trnh x l n hng rt ngn Lead time, thay v c gng nhp thm hng tr.

  1. So snh hiu sut gia cc m hnh hc my: u l phng php ti u d bo tng doanh s?

Kt qu phn tch tng quan cho thy ton b cc bin u vo u c h s thp. iu ny hm rng mi quan h gia cc bin gii thch v s lng bn ra khng phi dng tuyn tnh trc tip. Do , cc m hnh tuyn tnh nh Linear Regression hoc nhng m hnh gi nh cu trc tuyn tnh mnh nh ARIMA/SARIMAX s khng ph hp, bi chng da vo gi nh rng khi bin X tng/gim th bin Y s thay i tng ng theo mt quy lut tuyn tnh n nh.

Tuy nhin, d liu thc t thng cha cc dng quan h phi tuyn v tng tc gia nhiu bin. V d: gim gi c th ch tc ng mnh khi kt hp ng thi vi thi gian giao hng ngn; hoc tc ng ca th trng ch th hin r khi mc hot ng ca i th mc thp. y l nhng dng quan h m heatmap khng th th hin, nhng li rt ph bin trong d liu kinh doanh.

V vy, cc m hnh c kh nng hc c cu trc phi tuyn, ngng (threshold) v tng tc phc tp gia cc bin chng hn nh** Random Forest v XGBoost** l la chn ph hp hn. Nhng m hnh ny khng ph thuc vo tng quan tuyn tnh m khai thc c s kt hp gia cc yu t, phn nh chnh xc hn c ch hnh thnh doanh s trong thc t.

In[]:
df_ml = df_agg.copy()

# A. To Lags cho bin mc tiu (Target Lags)
#  ngha: Doanh s ca 1, 2, 3 thng trc nh hng n thng ny
df_ml['lag_1'] = df_ml['units_sold'].shift(1)
df_ml['lag_2'] = df_ml['units_sold'].shift(2)
df_ml['lag_3'] = df_ml['units_sold'].shift(3)
df_ml['lag_12'] = df_ml['units_sold'].shift(12) # So vi cng k nm ngoi

# B. To Rolling Mean (Trung bnh trt)
#  ngha: Xu hng trung bnh 3 thng gn nht
df_ml['rolling_mean_3'] = df_ml['units_sold'].shift(1).rolling(window=3).mean()

# C. Ly sai phn (Diff) -  bt s thay i thay v s tuyt i
df_ml['diff_1'] = df_ml['units_sold'].diff(1)

# D. Thm thng tin thi gian
df_ml['month'] = df_ml.index.month
df_ml['quarter'] = df_ml.index.quarter

# Loi b cc dng b NaN do qu trnh shift (to lag)
df_ml = df_ml.dropna()

print(f"D liu sau khi to features: {df_ml.shape}")
print("=== DANH SCH CC C TRNG (FEATURES) ===")
cols = df_ml.columns.tolist()
for i in range(0, len(cols), 3):
    print(", ".join(cols[i:i+3]))

# Tch bin X v y
target = 'units_sold'
features = [col for col in df_ml.columns if col not in [target]]

X = df_ml[features]
y = df_ml[target]

# Chia theo thi gian (Khng c shuffle)
test_size = 12
X_train, X_test = X.iloc[:-test_size], X.iloc[-test_size:]
y_train, y_test = y.iloc[:-test_size], y.iloc[-test_size:]
# === PHN THNG BO ===
print("-" * 30)
print("KT QU CHIA TP D LIU (TRAIN/TEST SPLIT)")
print("-" * 30)

# 1. Thng tin tp Train
print(f"1. Tp Hun luyn (Train set):")
print(f"   - Kch thc: {X_train.shape}")
# Dng .date()  ch ly ngy thng nm, b gi pht cho gn
print(f"   - Thi gian:  T [{X_train.index.min().date()}] n [{X_train.index.max().date()}]")

print("\n") # Xung dng cho thong

# 2. Thng tin tp Test
print(f"2. Tp Kim tra (Test set):")
print(f"   - Kch thc: {X_test.shape}")
print(f"   - Thi gian:  T [{X_test.index.min().date()}] n [{X_test.index.max().date()}]")

print("-" * 30)
print(f"T l Test size: {len(X_test) / len(X) * 100:.1f}% trn tng d liu")

# n_estimators: S lng cy
# learning_rate: Tc  hc (thp th chm nhng chc)
# max_depth:  su ca cy (trnh overfitting)
params_manual = {
    'n_estimators': 1000,      # Gim v 1000 ( dng)
    'learning_rate': 0.05,     # Gi nguyn
    'max_depth': 3,            # Gim v 5 (Trnh hc qu su vo chi tit nhiu)
    'random_state': 42,
    'n_jobs': -1,
    'early_stopping_rounds': 50
}
model = XGBRegressor(**params_manual)

model.fit(X_train, y_train,
          eval_set=[(X_train, y_train), (X_test, y_test)],
          verbose=False)

df_ml = df_agg.copy()

# A. To Lags cho bin mc tiu (Target Lags)
#  ngha: Doanh s ca 1, 2, 3 thng trc nh hng n thng ny
df_ml['lag_1'] = df_ml['units_sold'].shift(1)
df_ml['lag_2'] = df_ml['units_sold'].shift(2)
df_ml['lag_3'] = df_ml['units_sold'].shift(3)
df_ml['lag_12'] = df_ml['units_sold'].shift(12) # So vi cng k nm ngoi

# B. To Rolling Mean (Trung bnh trt)
#  ngha: Xu hng trung bnh 3 thng gn nht
df_ml['rolling_mean_3'] = df_ml['units_sold'].shift(1).rolling(window=3).mean()

# C. Ly sai phn (Diff) -  bt s thay i thay v s tuyt i
df_ml['diff_1'] = df_ml['units_sold'].diff(1)

# D. Thm thng tin thi gian
df_ml['month'] = df_ml.index.month
df_ml['quarter'] = df_ml.index.quarter

# Loi b cc dng b NaN do qu trnh shift (to lag)
df_ml = df_ml.dropna()

cols = df_ml.columns.tolist()
for i in range(0, len(cols), 3):
    print(", ".join(cols[i:i+3]))

print(" ang chy Grid Search cho Random Forest (Vui lng i)...")

# nh ngha li tham s cn th
param_grid = {
    'n_estimators': [300,500],
    'max_depth': [3,5],
    'min_samples_leaf': [2,3,4],
    'max_features': [None]
}

# Thit lp Cross-Validation cho chui thi gian
tscv = TimeSeriesSplit(n_splits=3)
rf_base = RandomForestRegressor(random_state=42, n_jobs=-1)

# Chy tm kim
grid_search = GridSearchCV(estimator=rf_base,
                           param_grid=param_grid,
                           cv=tscv,
                           scoring='neg_mean_squared_error',
                           verbose=1)
grid_search.fit(X_train, y_train)

# Ly m hnh tt nht
best_params = grid_search.best_params_
print(f" Tham s tt nht: {best_params}")

model = RandomForestRegressor(**best_params, random_state=42, n_jobs=-1)
model.fit(X_train, y_train)

)
